{"tid":1173642,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"廢老擋門等朋友　車長勸落車反被罵「咩態度」","createTime":"2019-05-27T09:12:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-27T09:34:50.000Z","uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0a6273f66dea9907be3a71b898bda581c3a94c75","tid":1173642,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T09:12:55.000Z","msg":"廢老擋門等朋友 車長勸落車反被罵「咩態度」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2K8qrm2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2K8qrm2&d=I3HUAc%2BVzuGSjYFa2O0dWNOJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=88bbbad7\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2K8qrm2</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190527/photo/bkn-20190527153013053-0527_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190527161304\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190527%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190527153013053-0527_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190527161304&h=6a51d666&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n阻住成車人？<br />\n<br />\n星期日（26日）下午約3時，有廢老趁巴士埋站期間衝上車，擋在車門前與友人對話。車長見狀直呼︰「落番車啦！你等人嘛，架車要開呀小姐」。<br />\n<br />\n惟她聞言頓時火起︰「咩事呀？咩叫落番車呀？」她更反指車長態度欠佳︰「咁你可以問一問呀嘛，唔係一句叫我落番車嘛」。"},{"pid":"7ec7618588555933667a7898e010762d388ba438","tid":1173642,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T09:13:30.000Z","msg":"個司機仲叫條廢老做<span style=\"color: red;\">小姐</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7416d227ca2dc5f82550f1ac116162a71723b805","tid":1173642,"uid":52605,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T09:22:17.000Z","msg":"成日都有啲咁嘅人等佢啲老友<br />\n但係佢個老友唔係幾步 係半條街距離"},{"pid":"59388749b7e518b186e50d1e2aa1249ba8bb8c6f","tid":1173642,"uid":79798,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0a6273f66dea9907be3a71b898bda581c3a94c75","tid":1173642,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T09:12:55.000Z","msg":"廢老擋門等朋友 車長勸落車反被罵「咩態度」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2K8qrm2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.